## ROYAL MASTER DEGREE | The Obligation.
%SPACE
%IMAGE "figures/14-rm-obligation.png" 26

%SPACE
When K._S. gives three raps, the Cherubim will form about
the altar precisely as before, after which K._S. and H._K._T. will
descend from the dais and enter the ring of Cherubim
through the opening east of the altar.

After the obligation, K._S. raps the gavel and |
the Cherubim dissolve as before. (Refer back to Fig. 7).

%PAGE
